      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Determinazione valore statistico [fit]                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Input: record [fit]                                       *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       det-vls-fit-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione totale netto documento           *
      *              *                                                 *
      *              * Attenzione:                                     *
      *              * la determinazione del totale netto fattura-     *
      *              * to tiene conto delle attualio personalizza-     *
      *              * zioni per le statistiche; vale a dire:          *
      *              * - detrazione dello sconto in chiusura           *
      *              * - non detrazione dello sconto pagamento         *
      *              * - non detrazione delle spese aggiuntive         *
      *              * - non detrazione delle spese incasso            *
      *              * - non detrazione delle spese bollo              *
      *              * - accumulo delle righe di addebito              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       rf-fit-tot-rig (01)
                     rf-fit-tot-rig (02)
                     rf-fit-tot-rig (03)
                     rf-fit-tot-rig (04)
                     rf-fit-tot-rig (05)
                     rf-fit-tot-rig (06)
                     rf-fit-tot-rig (07)
                     rf-fit-tot-rig (08)
                     rf-fit-tot-rig (09)
                                        giving w-det-vls-fit-tne      .
           subtract  rf-fit-tot-scc       from w-det-vls-fit-tne      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Totale righe 1                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-fit-tot-rig (01)  to   w-det-vls-fit-tr1      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sconto in chiusura                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-fit-tot-scc       to   w-det-vls-fit-scc      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Sconto pagamento                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-fit-tot-scp       to   w-det-vls-fit-scp      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione totale cumulativo documento      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-det-vls-fit-tne    to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           subtract  rf-fit-tot-scp       from w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           if        rf-fit-spe-snx (1)   =    1
                     add  rf-fit-spe-imp (1)
                                          to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           if        rf-fit-spe-snx (2)   =    1
                     add  rf-fit-spe-imp (2)
                                          to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           if        rf-fit-spe-snx (3)   =    1
                     add  rf-fit-spe-imp (3)
                                          to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           if        rf-fit-spe-snx (4)   =    1
                     add  rf-fit-spe-imp (4)
                                          to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           if        rf-fit-spe-snx (5)   =    1
                     add  rf-fit-spe-imp (5)
                                          to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           if        rf-fit-spe-snx (6)   =    1
                     add  rf-fit-spe-imp (6)
                                          to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           add       rf-fit-tot-sic       to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           add       rf-fit-tot-sia       to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
           add       rf-fit-tot-spb       to   w-det-vls-fit-tcu      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione castelletto iva                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-det-vls-fit-ibl      .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-vls-fit-imp      .
           move      zero                 to   w-det-vls-fit-ctr      .
       det-vls-fit-310.
           add       1                    to   w-det-vls-fit-ctr      .
           if        w-det-vls-fit-ctr    >    6
                     go to det-vls-fit-320.
           if        rf-fit-iva-cod
                    (w-det-vls-fit-ctr)   =    zero
                     go to det-vls-fit-310.
           add       rf-fit-iva-ibl
                    (w-det-vls-fit-ctr)   to   w-det-vls-fit-ibl      .
           add       rf-fit-iva-imp
                    (w-det-vls-fit-ctr)   to   w-det-vls-fit-imp      .
           go to     det-vls-fit-310.
       det-vls-fit-320.
           add       w-det-vls-fit-ibl
                     w-det-vls-fit-imp  giving w-det-vls-fit-tot      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione importo righe di addebito quale  *
      *              * differenza tra totale cumulato finora  e totale *
      *              * imponibile                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           subtract  w-det-vls-fit-tcu    from w-det-vls-fit-ibl
                                        giving w-det-vls-fit-rda      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Aggiornamento totale netto con totale addebiti  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       w-det-vls-fit-rda    to   w-det-vls-fit-tne      .
       det-vls-fit-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eventuale conversione in valuta base            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su codice valuta                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
